name: Queen Size Mattress, clean and bagged (curb alert) (Wicker Park)
description:
Queen size mattress from Ikea. No stains. No bed bugs. Totally clean. Just didn't need it after moving and no donation sites accept mattresses.
I covered it in two plastic mattress bags and taped it, so it should still be clean despite being dragged into an alley. Located near apartment at 1440 N Ashland. Behind building in alley.
If you are interested in the bedframe for it, shoot me a message. I have all the parts and pieces packaged together.
